---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="NEET Study Environment | Jyoti Girls PG near Osmanpura"
  description="Jyoti Girls PG near Osmanpura offers silent study zones, mentoring, and coaching access tailored for NEET aspirants."
>

  <section style="padding: 60px 0 40px; background: var(--color-bg-base);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Hostel for NEET Students</span>
      <h1 class="section-heading">NEET Study Environment</h1>
      <p class="section-lead">Jyoti Girls PG is purpose-built for NEET aspirants who need disciplined schedules, strong supervision, and the shortest commute to Osmanpura coaching classes.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Focused Study Infrastructure</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Silent Library Floor</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Ergonomic desks, pin-drop silence, and power backup ensure uninterrupted revision till midnight.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Smart Room Layouts</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Rooms are organised with personal study tables, task lighting, and storage so each resident has a private prep corner.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Exam Mock Zone</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Weekly mock tests are conducted in our seminar room with OMR sheets and invigilation to mimic centre conditions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-subtle);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Academic Mentoring &amp; Tracking</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:20px;max-width:600px;">
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Subject mentors from Osmanpura institutes host doubt clinics twice a week.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Progress dashboards capture test scores, attendance, and focus areas for targeted improvement.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Dedicated quiet hours after dinner reserve time for last-mile revision.</li>
        <li style="color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:10px;">Parents get fortnightly performance updates and behavioural reports.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: var(--color-bg-white);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Location Advantage for NEET Aspirants</h2>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:20px;margin-bottom:40px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Walk to Coaching</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Resonance, Aakash, and local NEET academies around Osmanpura are within 5–10 minutes on foot, saving travel time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Healthy Daily Routine</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Early breakfast, curated snacks, and hydration stations keep energy levels steady during back-to-back classes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Peer Accountability</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.88rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);">Residents preparing for similar exams motivate each other, share resources, and maintain discipline.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <button class="btn-primary" data-modal="availability">Book a counselling call</button>
        <a href="https://wa.me/919922333305?text=Hello%20Jyoti%20Girls%20PG%2C%20please%20share%20details%20about%20your%20NEET%20study%20support." class="btn-whatsapp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Request details on WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
